# Must match APP_SHARED_SECRET on the backend (see backend/.env.example) -
# sent as X-App-Secret on crash reports. Baked into the JS bundle at build
# time, so it only stops opportunistic abuse of the endpoint, not someone who
# decompiles the APK. Leave unset to send no header (backend then allows the
# request unless it has its own secret configured).
EXPO_PUBLIC_APP_SHARED_SECRET=
